Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(419.596,436.667)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here they come, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常感谢  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, madam
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel so alive
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富财富  发财致富
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cha-ching, cha-ching, cha-chingaree
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.78,0:01:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金钱金钱  我好爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, oh, money, how I love thee
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.52,0:01:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富财富  发财致富
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cha-ching, cha-chong, cha-changaroo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从分到元  多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From pennies to dollars any amount'll do
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富财富  没有角逐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cha-ching, cha-ching, it's no contest
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.03,0:01:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最爱的  只有一个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing that I love the best
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从看到的壮丽景象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From every sight I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到听见的美妙天籁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the sweetest sound I've heard
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我乐意放弃掉一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd gladly give up everything
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.55,0:01:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不惜代价赚到钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For all the money that I've earned
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富财富  发财致富
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cha-ching, cha-ching, cha-chingaree
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上一切  比不过贪心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on earth like the feeling of greed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on earth
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.44,0:02:08.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比不过贪心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:08.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like the feeling of greed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't do that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看彩色玻璃高脚凳可以放这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think the stained-glass barstool can go over here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麂皮手工雕刻木制运动旗帜展示柜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the pseudo hand-carved
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wooden sports flag display case
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以放那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can go over there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.67,0:02:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三位你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there, matey
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要给你们什么服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help you gentlemen with something?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟店主谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak to the owner
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们算老几
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,容我自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霍华德白兰地  白兰地经销公司总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howard Blandy, President
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Blandy Franchising Company
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霍华德白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howard Blandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说那个霍华德白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean the Howard Blandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是那个策划进行无情接管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Howard Blandy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that masterminded the ruthless takeover
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村所有个体经营餐厅的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of every small, family-owned business in Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个霍华德白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Howard Blandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I worship you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,振作起来  小伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it together a little, man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  单纯只是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's just that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你富得流油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're rich
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么风把你吹来蟹堡王的  霍华德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To what do I owe the honor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of having you at the Krusty Krab, Howard?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从你这收购蟹堡王要出多少价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would it take to buy the Krusty Krab from you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收购蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王不是拿来卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not for sale
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我可能搞不出来你那种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I may not make as much
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奢侈得要死的那种连锁餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as your fancy-schmancy mega restaurant chain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这是整天辛劳的血汗与泪水的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's the blood, sweat and tears of a hard day's work
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不是给点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not about the
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy sweet mother of pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.56,0:03:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢你的思考方式  白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like the way you think, Blandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这一手提箱的钱还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it'll take a lot more than a suitcase full of cash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可没法从我手上买走蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to buy the Krusty Krab from me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱还有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more than that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剩下的在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rest is over there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumping King Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交  能拿钱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sold, can I have my money?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个条件  签订这份合同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one thing, if you can sign this contract
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表明你转让蟹堡王以及其所有权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It just states that you relinquish the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all ownership thereof
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有其员工  商品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,along with its employees, merchandise
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,商标  收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,logos and cash registers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还能拿到钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still get the money?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be fine then
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我给我给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, give me, give me, give me, give me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you 'round
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  他们在蟹堡王挂三角旗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, they're putting up pennants in the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm retiring
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Retiring?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以想做什么就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free to do whatever I want
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以学骑我30年前买的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can learn how to ride that bicycle I got 30 years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者去逛市中心新开的鱼钩博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or go to the new hook museum downtown
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以画碗装的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or ever paint bowls of fruit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不该替我高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.91,0:04:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure am
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你开心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天都知道我不会替他高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heaven knows I won't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.87,0:04:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两位好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是卡尔  你们的新经理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Carl, I'll be your new manager
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新经理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New manager?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在周一蟹堡工作的工作体验
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find working at the Krabby O'Mondays
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必定会寓教于乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be both a learning experience and an enjoyable one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周一蟹堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby O'Mondays?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些玩意再也用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't need these anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你们的新制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, here are your new uniforms
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and here are the
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工手册
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,employee manuals
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天早上再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you first thing tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新一天的甜美香气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sweet smell of a brand new day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一站  新开的鱼钩博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First stop, the new hook museum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(842.17,330)}周一蟹堡
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I'll
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周一蟹堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby O'Mondays?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不取这种名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the name I would've chosen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过都已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's all behind me now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(515.716,306)}鱼钩博物馆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地水域发现J形三叉鱼钩的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The three-pronged J hook
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was first sighted in local water
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早于一百多年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more than one hundred years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我讨厌高尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate golf
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  我想做的事情全都做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've done everything I wanted to do
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果连中午都还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's not even noon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看到她穿的鞋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see the shoes she had on?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So last-year
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别挂  吉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Gina
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.18,0:05:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.41,0:05:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What're you up to?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking on the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.41,0:05:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  你就没有正事要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad, isn't there something you need to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, actually I was hoping
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟你一起做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you and I could do something together
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去找工作  找爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a job, get a hobby
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么就找朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or get some friends
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她说要找朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get some friends, she says
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她说要找爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Find a hobby, she says
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她说要找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a job, she says
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1090.515,596)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,招聘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Help Wanted"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(657.914,414)}周一蟹堡
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三位你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there, mateys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临周一蟹堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krabby O'Mondays
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能先开始给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I start you off with
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以唱周一蟹堡生日歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sing the Krabby Monday's birthday song
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的小寿星听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my special little man?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日生日快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟你单独谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们周一蟹堡的座右铭是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's our motto here at Krabby O'Mondays?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真诚服务  面带微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Sincere service with a smile"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过也要有周一蟹堡精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but with the Krabby O'Mondays spirit
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥啊  你该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Squidward, you wouldn't want
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想跟人事部那边的谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to have to talk to Human Resources
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.94,0:07:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么座右铭是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what's our motto again?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真诚服务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sincere service
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面带微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a smile
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你可算会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're getting it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退休到头来也没好到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Retirement ain't all it's cracked up to be
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就来当洗碗工了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'm the new busboy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, son
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可要吓坏我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're starting to creep me out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会回来  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come back, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just knew you would
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  继续工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boy, back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不是你老板了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not your boss anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我尤金就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just call me Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.07,0:07:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你介意帮我擦一下桌子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you mind clearing this table for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道不  我从来没看过你这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I've never seen you so happy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被监视了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're watching us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙就是很讨厌  对吧章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy's a real pain in the hindquarters, hey, Squiddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  我觉得你要再看下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, I think you need to look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工手册的第20页
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at page 20 of our employee handbook again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才用不着卡尔定的笨规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need Carl's silly rules
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的觉得你应该要看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really think you should look
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(742.031,516)}救命
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Help me"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位啊  这边是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, fellas, what's going on over here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Carl
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在提醒尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just reminding Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.15,0:08:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工手册的第24条第3款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of article 24, section three of the employee handbook
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少说话  多上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Cut the chatter and pick up a platter"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对真正的章鱼哥动了什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you done with the real Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  你知道得越少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The less you know, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.16,0:08:39.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the better
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728.011,518)}合成堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:51.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112.545,276)}注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1128.568,852)}上菜
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the love?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力跟他们说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他们就是不听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but they wouldn't listen to me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直下流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is obscene
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to have a word
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.69,0:09:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您的零钱是一块七毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your change is $1.75
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自动收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Automated cash register?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡尔  你对我餐厅都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Carl, what have you done with me restaurant?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加工过的蟹黄堡  计算机化的收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Processed Krabby Patties, computerized registers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你这周围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look around you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的客人很满足于
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our customers are quite content
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种不自然  这种中规中矩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the contrived and the mediocre
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是因为他们不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because they don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己是在吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what they're eating
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  美女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道你吃的蟹黄堡里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you know what's in that Krabby Patty you're eating?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.05,0:09:44.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:44.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了你那种障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without all your smoke and mirrors
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没有人会吃这种垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no one would stomach this garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd he say?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Garbage?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.08,0:10:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  你己经违约了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, you're in violation of your contract
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,规矩是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rules
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你一条规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a rule for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让人吃彩色玻璃高脚凳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,people can't eat stained-glass barstools
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你看看什么叫自动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you automated
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白兰地先生  红色警报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Blandy, code red--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由思想家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free thinker
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  这里有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, is there a problem here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最好要相信有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better believe there's a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从前会亲吻你走过的地面  白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used to kiss the ground you walked on, Blandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可看到这一幕之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but after seeing this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连痰都不屑朝你那边吐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even spit in your direction
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡应该要亲手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties are supposed to be made by hand--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个一个做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one at a time--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,888)}合成堡
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是搁传送带上做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not on a conveyer belt
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我是不是不能加薪了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this mean I won't get that raise, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只好把它卖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to sell it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能回一点点本都能算运气好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be lucky if we get a fraction of what we paid for it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要以全价买下蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it for full price
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sold
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也用不着你的合同了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We won't need your contract anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴跟您一起做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice doing business with you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倍感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pleasure's all mine
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚出我的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get out of me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we did it, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王又回到我们手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is ours again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道  我发了这么一场怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, in that fit of maniacal rage
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能毁掉了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may have destroyed the restaurant,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓跑了所有的客人  逼到我们破产
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scared away all our customers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and forced us into bankruptcy--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为卖这破店的钱基本还回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I returned
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nearly every penny I sold this stink-heap for--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这一切都很值得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it was all worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我又重新得到了好朋友的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I got back the love of me dear friends
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错  不完全真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not really
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.94,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(142,192)}爱笑海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(227.316,446)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(487.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:12:00.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(407.566,442)\frz29.52}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(529.736,692)\frz29.08}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(433.602,542)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想搞什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.75,0:12:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班时间到了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for work, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天也要挣钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挣几个子还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like another nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天也要挣几个子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没那么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not that funny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830.523,234.8)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为真实  所以好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny because it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便车搭完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carpool's over
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几个子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的餐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your food
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没那么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not that funny
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你快住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please make it stop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(749.388,814)}开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(749.388,814)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward, see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时刻检查零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And always check for spare change
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天也要挣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几个子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天也要挣几个子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别笑了  折磨精
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cease your laughing, tormentor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This could be my chance
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你看起来很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you don't look well
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should sit down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.28,0:14:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你发烧了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're burning up, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身子侧面疼不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have your sides been hurting?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是有点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs60\pos(882.225,920)}94{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}摄氏度
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你体温居然有175度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And your temperature is 175 degrees
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.80,0:14:23.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是坏事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:23.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非你最近老是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unless you've been doing a lot of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最近确实老是笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have been laughing a lot lately
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你必须要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you've got to be careful
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然会把笑声囊烧坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to burn out your laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑声囊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My laughbox?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  那是你的身体部位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's the part of your body
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你发出笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that enables laughter
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是长期过度不停使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you use it too long without giving it a break
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会发烧  然后你就再也笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it burns out and you can never laugh again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是这样的吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what happened to you, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.66,0:14:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝你听好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is serious
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是把笑声囊烧伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you burn out your laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.58,0:15:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这辈子就再也笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll live your whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without ever laughing again
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  想不想听个笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, you want to hear a joke?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.63,0:15:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  我要大笑一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd love a good laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(748.039,922)}有 苍 蝇
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有四个轮子还会飞的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What has four wheels and flies?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A garbage truck
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能把我笑声囊烧伤了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to burn out my laughbox, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.61,0:15:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最重要的事情就是不要再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the most important thing is to stop laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何一种笑都可能会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any laugh at all could be dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要不笑多久才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long do I have to avoid laughing?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少应该要后半天都不笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd say at least the rest of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你最好要24小时不笑保平安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you better go 24 hours just to be safe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太谢谢你了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没你我都不知道要咋办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd do without you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一整天不笑只是一点小小的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A day without laughter is a small price to pay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才能保护笑声囊不被彻底摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to save my laughbox from utter destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要时刻警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must remain vigilant
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边没有好笑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing funny over there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边没有好笑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing funny over here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近过得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,香蕉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,banana peel--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.35,0:16:01.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:01.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.90,0:16:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please stop
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先走右脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right foot first
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.99,0:16:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我不能笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I can't laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道要怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常这样明明能笑翻他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That usually knocks him out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,控制住自己  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a grip on yourself, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你控制得住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in control
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离放屁坐垫远一点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just back away from the whoopie cushion, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,740)}放屁坐垫
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心那辆装派的卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out for that pie truck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(589.819,512)}派
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:58.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850.181,816)}正在驶离裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边没有好笑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing funny up here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可为了安全起见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But just to be safe
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经成功实现24小时不笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it 24 hours without laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's odd
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've lost my laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've lost my laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.07,0:17:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's terrible, Patrick--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不能笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't laugh anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一天都没有笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I went a whole day without laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我就笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now my laugh is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's dark in here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得点根火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better light a match
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(433.602,412)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就来对地方了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've come to the right place, son
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有样东西总能让我笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, there's one thing that always makes me laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看它不觉得好笑吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't it just tickle you, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.15,0:18:16.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不大觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not really
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来得用极端措施
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This calls for drastic measures
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我平时一般不会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't usually do this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你好像很迫切需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you seem desperate
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touch it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我想的还要糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is worse than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟钱可是欢乐的终极源头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, money is the ultimate source of joy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许应该要去问珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should ask Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她是科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's a scientist
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用科学来处理就简单了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's easy if you approach it scientifically, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what is laughter?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.68,0:18:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它曾向我的一生给予意义和目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The thing that used to give my life meaning and purpose
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可现在却在用冷酷无情来嘲弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but now mocks me with its cruel indifference
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是从科学上来讲  之所以会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But scientifically speaking, it's caused by
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为会厌导致你的喉咙收紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your epiglottis constricting your larynx
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使得进气不规则而呼吸紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,causing irregular air intake and respiratory upset
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds painful
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学会让一切都听起来疼  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Science makes everything sound painful, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你一点幽默理论课本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, here's some humor-theory textbooks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大笑力学  还有量子傻笑理论
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,laugh mechanics and the quantum giggle theory
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下倒是安静多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure is peaceful around here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟海绵宝宝变得不中用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since SquarePants became a sad sack
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我书都看完了  还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've read all the books, and still nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该再也笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll never laugh again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真不想看到那小子难过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really hate to see the little guy so sad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我更不想看人家高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not as much as I hate to see him happy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,之后在同一天晚上
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发现比起他笑声更难听的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I found the one thing I hate more than his laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟早能哭累他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll cry himself out soon
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场把戏必须要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This charade has to end
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别鬼哭狼嚎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this infernal crying has to stop
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可章鱼哥  我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Squidward, I
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我伤到了笑声囊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I broke my laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  根本就没有笑声囊这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, there's no such thing as a laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我编出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made the whole thing up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你才不会瞎笑  我才能静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get some peace from your insipid laughter
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我的笑声囊没被伤到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean my laughbox isn't broken?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你完全就是存心骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it was a cruel lie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我一下子抑郁过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that sent me into spiraling depression?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这么说好像确实挺残忍  不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, it sounds pretty harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you put it that way, but
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都可以笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could laugh the whole time?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.15,0:20:56.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:56.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really fell for it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I did
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.12,0:21:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连体温计泡热油那套都能让你上当
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You even fell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the old thermometer-in- the-boiling-oil routine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的没那么好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not really that funny, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's hilarious
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄伤笑声囊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Break your laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a schlemiel
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  他醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, he's waking up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.99,0:21:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你住院了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in the hospital, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把笑声囊弄伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You broke your laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生说这笑声囊最小最干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The doctor said it was the most tiny, dried out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.15,0:21:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,利用最不充分  行医生涯中前所未见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,underused laughbox he'd ever laid eyes on
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.74,0:22:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以医生就割了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So they cut it out
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.55,0:22:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,割了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.21,0:22:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to see it?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇一摇看它弹来弹去还挺好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's fun to shake it up and watch it bounce around
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.76,0:22:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也笑不出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can never laugh again?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该能笑得更厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your laugh should be stronger than ever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你们明明把我笑声囊割了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you cut out my laughbox
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  但你一位朋友慷慨地让我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, but one of your friends has generously allowed us
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把自己的笑声囊移植一部分给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to transplant part of theirs to you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.83,0:22:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生不给钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't pay me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离答案越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're getting warmer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你笑得好像我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You laugh just like me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他去跟这个世界共享欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he goes, off to share his laughter with the world
